➜【星连文学社】宽哥：《西江月》
http://www.sohu.com/a/414427098_100115135	40591
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200822/fe05a4ac7da44d7b8bf4dc2b22739adf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> <strong>《西江月》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong> 文/宽哥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">楼外流光溢彩，席前情烈隆声。少年往事是豪英，樽满频频相庆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不觉月沉人醉，殷勤珍重聆听。浮生一梦尽虚荣，流水画桥花径。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200822/4edbc93875c34459b0f2203c72594c3a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200822/51c9cdcb33cd4205963602a47753c770.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
