➜【星连文学社】彩虹：一次庆会
http://www.sohu.com/a/414432388_100115135	44370
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200822/86cfad71784a48eaa6def98ca4a1080b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一次庆会</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/彩虹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人生有几次巅峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">峰回路转遇到君</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看到您</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">神采奕奕笑容</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如夜晚的百合</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纯静，洁白，慈祥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">温馨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>您温婉的话</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>似一小片，一小片菱角叶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘来，轻飘飘扯来</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>真诚的语气</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>似一束光，塞满我</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>孤寂的心房</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>翻了唐诗三百首</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>读了普希金，拜伦，雪莱，泰戈尔诗</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《假如生活欺骗了你》</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
